Bank of Israel Weighs Further Mortgage Steps, Channel Two Says

-- B y   A l i s a   O d e n h e i m e r
-- 
2011-04-13T11:33:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/bank-of-israel-weighs-further-mortgage-steps-channel-two-says.html
The Bank of  Israel  may take further
steps to cool the housing market after the Passover holiday,
Channel Two reported on its website, without saying where it got
the information. The central bank may limit mortgages to 50
percent of the value of the home, Channel Two reported. The
central bank declined to comment.       Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
